text: Viktorija Todorovska (born 26 November 2000) is a Macedonian cross-country skier. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Macedonian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of North Macedonia
